crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Mallox Ransomware CnC Domain (whyers .io) in DNS Lookup
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET MALWARE Mallox Ransomware CnC Domain (whyers .io) in DNS Lookup"; dns.query; dotprefix; content:".whyers.io"; nocase; endswith; reference:url,blog.cyble.com/2023/06/22/mallox-ransomware-implements-new-infection-strategy/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2046826; rev:1; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2023_07_17, deployment Perimeter, malware_family mallox, performance_impact Low, signature_severity Major, tag Ransomware, updated_at 2023_07_17;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Observed Mallox Ransomware Domain (whyers .io) in TLS SNI
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tls $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Observed Mallox Ransomware Domain (whyers .io) in TLS SNI"; flow:established,to_server; tls.sni; dotprefix; content:".whyers.io"; endswith; fast_pattern; reference:url,blog.cyble.com/2023/06/22/mallox-ransomware-implements-new-infection-strategy/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2046827; rev:1; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2023_07_17, deployment Perimeter, malware_family mallox, performance_impact Low, signature_severity Major, tag Ransomware, updated_at 2023_07_17;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: SERVER-OTHER Squid HTTP Vary response header denial of service attempt
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"SERVER-OTHER Squid HTTP Vary response header denial of service attempt"; flow:to_client,established; http_header; content:"Vary|3A|"; content:!"|0D 0A|",within 250; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:http; reference:cve,2016-2569; reference:url,www.squid-cache.org/Advisories/SQUID-2016_2.txt; classtype:denial-of-service; sid:41379; rev:1; )
